=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />直接話說三道四咪算囉"},{"pid":"6554944a86bd84b742f3d6f6a8ed1611158c72ee","tid":2039166,"uid":322732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T01:28:06.000Z","msg":"即係好撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff931145632d71733d8863c793b4fa660c6487b7","tid":2039166,"uid":67816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T01:28:13.000Z","msg":"篇文寫得咁撚差搵支那人寫架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"ae44d5e3126a154d1f34245b657fe3c8bffcdce1","tid":2039166,"uid":67816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"578d5dd9d8d7654b942299155619564053965112","tid":2039166,"uid":53481,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T01:27:37.000Z","msg":"「<span style=\"color: red;\">絕大部分</span>守法的香港人，包括海外投資者，無需為此擔心。」<br />\n唔係所有守法的香港人可以放心，明白晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T01:29:45.000Z","msg":"咁都唔敢100%肯定<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n港共：守法既人都有機會犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"990f2d20b6ea8025c84acf33b0c5185a2806f1f9","tid":2039166,"uid":32665,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T01:25:18.000Z","msg":"去你妈的！ 咱们有强大的祖国作为后盾 怕什么呀？<br />\n 美国人 美国企业 全给我滚出去！ 夹着尾巴逃走吧弓！  666<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}}